KAON2 is a light-weight Description Locig reasoner based on Java.

It's an excellent software, however poor documented. Only some basic functions are comprehensively documented.

Below are tips for some specific details in using KAON2. It's being logged during the process of developing an ontology-based project in Media Lab, PKU.

Hope you enjoy it.

Please visit the blog for more details on this code.
